<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Must-Buy Souvenirs | TaiwanMe</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="/image/logo.png" type="image/png">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
    <style>
        /* ========================================= */
        /* 1. Hero Banner (比照 Culture/Dining 規格) */
        /* ========================================= */
        .souvenir-hero {
            width: 100%;
            height: 40vh; 
            min-height: 300px;
            /* 請確認是否有這張圖，若無會顯示背景色 */
            background-image: url('/image/souvenirs/banner.png'); 
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            display: flex; 
            align-items: center; 
            justify-content: center;
            position: relative;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
            background-color: #333;
        }

        .souvenir-hero::after {
            content: ''; 
            position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; 
            width: 100%; height: 100%;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); 
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .souvenir-hero-content {
            position: relative; 
            z-index: 2; 
            text-align: center; 
            color: #fff;
        }

        .souvenir-title {
            font-family: var(--font-main);
            font-size: 3rem; 
            margin: 0; 
            text-transform: uppercase; 
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            font-weight: 900;
        }

        /* ========================================= */
        /* 2. Main Content Container */
        /* ========================================= */
        .content-container {
            max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto 100px; padding: 0 20px;
        }
        
        .intro-text-box {
            text-align: center; margin-bottom: 70px;
        }
        .intro-p {
            font-size: 1.15rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #555; max-width: 750px; margin: 0 auto;
        }

        /* ========================================= */
        /* 3. Souvenir Grid & Cards */
        /* ========================================= */
        .souvenir-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 40px;
        }

        .souvenir-card {
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            border: 1px solid #eee;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .souvenir-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            border-color: var(--accent-color);
        }

        .card-img-box {
            width: 100%;
            height: 220px;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }

        .card-img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: transform 0.6s ease;
        }

        .souvenir-card:hover .card-img {
            transform: scale(1.08);
        }

        .card-content {
            padding: 25px;
            flex-grow: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .card-cat {
            color: var(--accent-color);
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .card-title {
            font-family: var(--font-main);
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0 0 10px;
        }

        .card-desc {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        /* RWD */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .souvenir-hero { height: 250px; }
            .souvenir-title { font-size: 2rem; }
            .souvenir-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 30px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../partials/header') %>

    <div class="souvenir-hero">
        <div class="souvenir-hero-content">
            <h1 class="souvenir-title">SOUVENIRS</h1>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-container">
        
        <div class="intro-text-box">
            <p class="intro-p">
                Bringing a piece of Taiwan home is the best way to share your journey. From world-famous pastries to premium high-mountain tea, here are the most iconic gifts ("Omiyage") that locals love and travelers cherish.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="souvenir-grid">
            
            <div class="souvenir-card">
                <div class="card-img-box">
                    <img src="/image/souvenirs/pineapple_cake.jpg" alt="Pineapple Cake" class="card-img" onerror="this.src='https://placehold.co/600x400/eee/999?text=Pineapple+Cake'">
                </div>
                <div class="card-content">
                    <span class="card-cat">Pastry</span>
                    <h3 class="card-title">Pineapple Cake (鳳梨酥)</h3>
                    <p class="card-desc">
                        The undisputed king of Taiwanese souvenirs. Choose between the sweet traditional paste (winter melon mix) or the tart, fibrous native pineapple filling (Tuchong).
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="souvenir-card">
                <div class="card-img-box">
                    <img src="/image/souvenirs/tea.jpg" alt="Taiwanese Tea" class="card-img" onerror="this.src='https://placehold.co/600x400/eee/999?text=Oolong+Tea'">
                </div>
                <div class="card-content">
                    <span class="card-cat">Beverage</span>
                    <h3 class="card-title">Alishan Oolong Tea (高山茶)</h3>
                    <p class="card-desc">
                        Grown in the misty mountains of Alishan, this hand-picked tea is world-renowned for its creamy texture and floral aroma. A perfect gift for tea connoisseurs.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="souvenir-card">
                <div class="card-img-box">
                    <img src="/image/souvenirs/nougat.jpg" alt="Nougat" class="card-img" onerror="this.src='https://placehold.co/600x400/eee/999?text=Nougat'">
                </div>
                <div class="card-content">
                    <span class="card-cat">Snack</span>
                    <h3 class="card-title">French Nougat (牛軋糖)</h3>
                    <p class="card-desc">
                        A chewy, milky treat packed with crunchy almonds or peanuts. "Sugar & Spice" (糖村) is the most famous brand, known for using premium French butter.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="souvenir-card">
                <div class="card-img-box">
                    <img src="/image/souvenirs/suncake.jpg" alt="Sun Cake" class="card-img" onerror="this.src='https://placehold.co/600x400/eee/999?text=Sun+Cake'">
                </div>
                <div class="card-content">
                    <span class="card-cat">Pastry</span>
                    <h3 class="card-title">Taichung Sun Cake (太陽餅)</h3>
                    <p class="card-desc">
                        A round, flaky pastry with a sweet maltose filling. Originating from Taichung, it's best enjoyed with hot tea.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="souvenir-card">
                <div class="card-img-box">
                    <img src="/image/souvenirs/dried_fruit.jpg" alt="Dried Fruit" class="card-img" onerror="this.src='https://placehold.co/600x400/eee/999?text=Dried+Mango'">
                </div>
                <div class="card-content">
                    <span class="card-cat">Snack</span>
                    <h3 class="card-title">Dried Mango (愛文芒果乾)</h3>
                    <p class="card-desc">
                        Made from the famous Irwin (Aiwen) mangoes grown in Tainan. Chewy, fragrant, and purely natural without artificial sweeteners.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="souvenir-card">
                <div class="card-img-box">
                    <img src="/image/souvenirs/whisky.jpg" alt="Kavalan Whisky" class="card-img" onerror="this.src='https://placehold.co/600x400/eee/999?text=Kavalan+Whisky'">
                </div>
                <div class="card-content">
                    <span class="card-cat">Alcohol</span>
                    <h3 class="card-title">Kavalan Whisky (葛瑪蘭威士忌)</h3>
                    <p class="card-desc">
                        Taiwan's pride. This award-winning single malt whisky from Yilan has beaten Scottish brands in blind taste tests. A premium gift choice.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
    <script src="/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>